title: Ep. 321 - The Search For Jussie’s ‘Real’ Attackers
description:
Crooked Cook County drops charges against Jussie Smollett, AOC encourages senators not to vote for the legislation she wrote and they co-sponsored, and David Brooks draws a moral equivalence between Russia hoaxers and the Russia hoaxed in the New York Times. Date: 03-27-2019
